            "title": "《美指期貨》道瓊斯指數期貨現升0.37%,報42524",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社6日專訊》截至香港時間17:05,<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道指</a>期貨升155點或0.37%,報42524點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　納指期貨升76.8點或0.36%,報21659點。</p></section><section><p class=\"\">　</p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　標普500指數期貨升23.5點或0.4%,報5969.5點。(rc)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
